name: compiler_deep_v8_while_adds_generated_value_1_times
section: control-loop-mutation-v8
args: a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: while loop with generated accumulator should execute exactly 1 times.
law: (= (with [i 0 acc {a}] (do (while (< i 1) (begin (set! acc (+ acc {b})) (set! i (+ i 1)))) acc)) (+ {a} {b}))
